拷打，拷问；动刑；虐待；拷打出：
The secret police tortured him to obtain information.

折磨；使痛苦；使苦恼：
The student was tortured with anxiety.

He was tortured by guilt.
他因内疚而感到痛苦。

歪曲；曲解(意见、论点等)：
They tortured my words.
他们曲解了我的话。
使扭曲；使变形：
the trees tortured by the wind
